00:04:32.188 --> 00:04:34.733 position:50% align:center
[BOTH]
Huh?

00:04:34.816 --> 00:04:39.404 position:50% align:center
I'm not sure. Although!
I know I want it to be fun!

00:04:39.487 --> 00:04:40.905 position:50% align:center
