00:04:40.989 --> 00:04:42.866 position:50% align:center
I think we can
all agree on that.

00:04:42.949 --> 00:04:45.326 position:50% align:center
For sure. Even if the audiences
we're performing for

00:04:45.410 --> 00:04:47.620 position:50% align:center
