another day. Right now...

00:04:56.755 --> 00:04:58.089 position:50% align:center
We need to train!

00:04:58.173 --> 00:04:59.883 position:50% align:center
Because whatever
we decide to do,

00:04:59.966 --> 00:05:01.426 position:50% align:center
we need to make it spectacular,

00:05:01.509 --> 00:05:03.720 position:50% align:center
or we'll disappoint
our loving fans!

00:05:03.803 --> 00:05:06.389 position:50% align:center
You mean like for
singing and dancing?

00:05:06.473 --> 00:05:08.016 position:50% align:center
[KANATA]
Dancing, huh...

00:05:08.099 --> 00:05:11.186 position:50% align:center
[AYUMU] I, personally, wouldn't
mind a singing lesson or two.

00:05:11.269 --> 00:05:12.520 position:50% align:center
All right.

00:05:12.604 --> 00:05:14.064 position:50% align:center
