focus on. Sound good?

00:05:16.900 --> 00:05:18.443 position:50% align:center
Yeah, that sounds perfect!

00:05:18.526 --> 00:05:21.404 position:50% align:center
[AI] Quick question! Is it
cool if we do everything?

00:05:21.488 --> 00:05:22.739 position:50% align:center
Fine by me.

00:05:22.822 --> 00:05:26.076 position:50% align:center
Oh, wow, talk about
exciting! Right?

00:05:26.159 --> 00:05:27.327 position:50% align:center
[RINA grunts]

00:05:28.661 --> 00:05:30.830 position:50% align:center
[KANATA groaning]

00:05:30.914 --> 00:05:32.791 position:50% align:center
