I think you can go further.

00:05:32.874 --> 00:05:34.542 position:50% align:center
You thought extremely wrong.

00:05:34.626 --> 00:05:37.712 position:50% align:center
[RINA grunting]

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:41.341 position:50% align:center
