00:05:41.424 --> 00:05:43.635 position:50% align:center
Apparently, it is.

00:05:43.718 --> 00:05:45.178 position:50% align:center
[BOTH groaning]

00:05:45.261 --> 00:05:46.763 position:50% align:center
[EMMA]
Dancers need to be flexible.

00:05:46.846 --> 00:05:49.057 position:50% align:center
So, you two are going
to have to work on that.

00:05:49.140 --> 00:05:50.350 position:50% align:center
While I'm thinking about it,

00:05:50.433 --> 00:05:51.851 position:50% align:center
I should thank you
for helping out.

00:05:51.935 --> 00:05:54.688 position:50% align:center
