00:06:17.585 --> 00:06:19.421 position:50% align:center
[KANATA, RINA exhale]

00:06:19.504 --> 00:06:20.964 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Heh.

00:06:22.340 --> 00:06:25.218 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:06:25.301 --> 00:06:27.429 position:50% align:center
Perfect. It's more
fun when you know

00:06:27.512 --> 00:06:29.973 position:50% align:center
