you're gonna be!

00:06:31.808 --> 00:06:33.685 position:50% align:center
Mm. I'll keep at it.

00:06:33.768 --> 00:06:36.312 position:50% align:center
It's no wonder she's
the Club Building Hero.

00:06:36.396 --> 00:06:37.439 position:50% align:center
Hero?

00:06:37.522 --> 00:06:38.815 position:50% align:center
So, you don't know?

00:06:38.898 --> 00:06:40.692 position:50% align:center
She's pretty well known
around here because

00:06:40.775 --> 00:06:42.777 position:50% align:center
