helping them out.

00:06:42.861 --> 00:06:44.612 position:50% align:center
Athletic clubs, that is.

00:06:44.696 --> 00:06:46.239 position:50% align:center
That's really neat!

00:06:46.322 --> 00:06:48.033 position:50% align:center
Speaking of helping out clubs...

00:06:48.116 --> 00:06:50.535 position:50% align:center
You helped reestablish ours,
but then didn't join,

00:06:50.618 --> 00:06:52.704 position:50% align:center
which was quite the curve ball.

00:06:52.787 --> 00:06:55.665 position:50% align:center
[KARIN] Hm? Because I
never intended to join.

00:06:55.749 --> 00:06:57.250 position:50% align:center
I just hated seeing
Emma depressed,

00:06:57.334 --> 00:06:59.419 position:50% align:center
