00:07:03.214 --> 00:07:04.424 position:50% align:center
Thank you, Karin.

00:07:04.507 --> 00:07:07.927 position:50% align:center
[gasps] It's not
that big of a deal.

00:07:08.011 --> 00:07:09.637 position:50% align:center
[AI laughs]

00:07:10.513 --> 00:07:15.685 position:50% align:center
[KASUMI] A-hem. It's time for
Kasumin's lecture to begin!

00:07:15.769 --> 00:07:17.437 position:50% align:center
Ooh! This sounds fun!

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:19.564 position:50% align:center
Where did those glasses
come from?

00:07:19.647 --> 00:07:23.902 position:50% align:center
