it is school idols need.

00:07:32.744 --> 00:07:34.412 position:50% align:center
Let's see. Um...

00:07:34.496 --> 00:07:37.916 position:50% align:center
The ability to express
themselves freely?

00:07:37.999 --> 00:07:39.167 position:50% align:center
Bingo!

00:07:39.250 --> 00:07:41.127 position:50% align:center
