Oh, I was just guessing.

00:07:41.211 --> 00:07:43.797 position:50% align:center
Now, this time I wanna
hear Tennoji's answer.

00:07:43.880 --> 00:07:47.384 position:50% align:center
What do all school idols need?

00:07:47.467 --> 00:07:49.678 position:50% align:center
Is it the ability to
connect with the people

00:07:49.761 --> 00:07:51.304 position:50% align:center
who support them?

00:07:51.388 --> 00:07:52.514 position:50% align:center
Exactly!

00:07:52.597 --> 00:07:54.432 position:50% align:center
We're both right, huh?

00:07:54.516 --> 00:07:55.975 position:50% align:center
[KASUMI]
Last up is Miyashita!

00:07:56.059 --> 00:07:58.144 position:50% align:center
Yes? [laughs]

00:07:58.228 --> 00:08:01.147 position:50% align:center
Beats me, I have no idea.

00:08:01.231 --> 00:08:05.193 position:50% align:center
Well, ring-a-ding-ding!
Because that's exactly right!

00:08:05.276 --> 00:08:06.611 position:50% align:center
It is?

00:08:06.695 --> 00:08:09.823 position:50% align:center
Come on, Shizuko.
You really don't know?

00:08:09.906 --> 00:08:11.408 position:50% align:center
[SHIZUKU gasps]

00:08:11.491 --> 00:08:12.701 position:50% align:center
It's a trick question.

00:08:12.784 --> 00:08:15.203 position:50% align:center
Cause there is no
"one correct answer."

00:08:15.286 --> 00:08:17.706 position:50% align:center
What school idols need is
to make the fans happy!

00:08:17.789 --> 00:08:20.583 position:50% align:center
So, if your answer could make
them smile, it was right.

00:08:20.667 --> 00:08:24.421 position:50% align:center
Wow. That was deep, who knew?

00:08:24.504 --> 00:08:26.798 position:50% align:center
Yay! You girls pass!

00:08:26.881 --> 00:08:29.467 position:50% align:center
â™ª

