[sighs]

00:08:30.802 --> 00:08:32.762 position:50% align:center
[AI laughing]

00:08:32.846 --> 00:08:34.889 position:50% align:center
Don't clap. I know
how awful that was.

00:08:34.973 --> 00:08:37.142 position:50% align:center
