You rocked!

00:08:37.225 --> 00:08:39.102 position:50% align:center
Yeah! I'm not exaggerating
when I say

00:08:39.185 --> 00:08:41.229 position:50% align:center
I just fell in love
with your singing!

00:08:41.312 --> 00:08:42.605 position:50% align:center
Your voice is great!

00:08:42.689 --> 00:08:45.316 position:50% align:center
