and then you'll be good to go!

00:08:45.400 --> 00:08:47.944 position:50% align:center
[sighs] I'll work on it.

00:08:48.028 --> 00:08:49.821 position:50% align:center
But you sounded super cute!

00:08:49.904 --> 00:08:51.781 position:50% align:center
O-Oh! You think so?

00:08:51.865 --> 00:08:53.908 position:50% align:center
Never thought our school
had a recording booth,

00:08:53.992 --> 00:08:56.161 position:50% align:center
yet here we are,
singing songs inside of one!

00:08:56.244 --> 00:08:58.246 position:50% align:center
