00:09:21.478 --> 00:09:24.856 position:50% align:center
Aw... But it's so cute.

00:09:24.939 --> 00:09:26.983 position:50% align:center
Uh. Wait.

00:09:27.067 --> 00:09:28.985 position:50% align:center
